{"tid":1000463,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[買新notebook]Samsung vs Mac vs Dell vs Fujitsu","createTime":"2019-01-29T12:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T07:24:02.000Z","uid":95519,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bf6f1b3347ae711803f3d93440302c6faa7b4a","tid":1000463,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:21:50.000Z","msg":"用左6年嘅lenovo撞爛咗個角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兼有時會自己熄機<br />\n新一年新氣象就諗住買新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係自己電腦知識唔夠<br />\n睇咗幾部啱心水嘅就上嚟問吓全能嘅連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n首先講吓我自己想要啲咩先<br />\n1. Budget ＄Max9500<br />\n2. 文書，睇戲<br />\n3. 可以用到4-6年<br />\n4. 想有touchmon<br />\n5. 13吋mon都夠<br />\n6. 可以用粵拼（唔係jyut個隻，係yuet呢隻）<br />\n7. 大啲儲存空間<br />\n8. 唔打機，唔剪片<br />\n9. RAM&gt;Harddisk&gt;靚唔靚仔&gt;方便＞唔易壞&gt;Mon<br />\n（CPU唔係幾識）<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n跟住講吓我睇咗啲心水<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Samsung Notebook 9 Pro (NP940X3N-K01HK)</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7imsvnj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7imsvnj.png&h=90bec88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5 處理器 8250U <br />\n．13.3&ldquo; FHD LED 觸控闊屏幕 (1920 x 1080)<br />\n．8 GB DDR4 RAM (BD 8 GB)<br />\n．256 GB SSD<br />\n．有touchmon<br />\n．豐澤做優惠＄8400左右<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Dell Inspiration 14 7472</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0VteO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0VteO4.png&h=f76538d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．第8代 Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-8550U 處理器 <br />\n．14.0 吋 FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS Truelife LED 背光顯示器<br />\n．8GB RAM, DDR4, 2400MHz; 最高至 16GB (額外記憶體獨立出售)<br />\n．128GB PCIe NVMe SSD + 1TB 5400 rpm Hard Drive<br />\n．無touchmon<br />\n．百老匯好似做$7000-8000左右<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">13吋Macbook Air</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqM8eO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqM8eO9.png&h=2900c99e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．1.6GHz 雙核心第 8 代 Intel Core i5 處理器<br />\n．Retina 顯示器<br />\n．8GB 2133MHz LPDDR3 記憶體<br />\n．128GB SSD 儲存<br />\n．無touchmon<br />\n．＄9499<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Fujitsu E548K501B</span></strong>[呢個係豐澤條友介紹嘅]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRiiB2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRiiB2z.png&h=3fc9a8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．Intel i5-8250U<br />\n．14吋mon<br />\n．上網check 4GB RAM，鋪頭寫8GB RAM<br />\n．256GB SSD<br />\n．無touchmon<br />\n．豐澤＄7800<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我自己鐘意samsung個部多啲<br />\n但係豐澤條友話行平板電好易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊啲apple fd又叫買mac<br />\n你哋會prefer邊部？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad38261cdd0e0e29759426ecb472f07fac3cd37a","tid":1000463,"uid":62532,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"唔好買mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非你玩音樂/畫圖<br />\n買laptop,  去果度再揀個靚仔既<br />\n建議你去黄金買會平好多"},{"pid":"82bbec15275557782f3d6498ceda5932a3db6ee5","tid":1000463,"uid":78429,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad38261cdd0e0e29759426ecb472f07fac3cd37a","tid":1000463,"uid":62532,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"唔好買mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n